com.wuest.prefab

Class ModRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wuest.prefab.ModRegistry
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientModRegistry

    public class ModRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the mod registry so there is a way to get to all instances of the blocks/items created by this mod.
    Author:
    WuestMan

        Gets the gui screen for the ID and passes position data to it.
        Parameters:
        id - The ID of the screen to get.
        x - The X-Axis of where this screen was created from, this is used to create a BlockPos.
        y - The Y-Axis of where this screen was created from, this is used to create a BlockPos.
        z - The Z-Axis of where this screen was created from, this is used to create a BlockPos.
        Returns:
        Null if the screen wasn't found, otherwise the screen found.
